Package frc.robot.subsystems

Class WheelOfFortune

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.robot.subsystems.WheelOfFortune
  • public class WheelOfFortune
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the code for the Wheel of Fortune manipulator. It initializes motor controllers and has methods for its various functions.
